<L>__{exterior roxbury street the war years day}
<A>__{it is a bright sunny day on a crowded street on the black side of boston. people and kids are busy with their own things. shorty bops his way down the street. he is a runty, very dark young man of 21 with a mission and a smile on his face. he wears the flamboyant style of the time: the whole zoot suit, pegged legs and a wide brim hat with a white feather stuck in the hat band.}
